&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage verification dashboards, bug tracking, and regression health&lt;/strong&gt; to provide clear visibility to program leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build, mentor, and scale&lt;/strong&gt; a high-performing team of verification and emulation engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive verification schedules and risk mitigation&lt;/strong&gt; aligned with chip program milestones and tapeout readiness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Represent verification and emulation in tapeout readiness reviews&lt;/strong&gt; and program-level decision forums&lt;/li&gt;
